quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  42,52,"Ko wano non Men wayayinir e maa…óa, ruuhu on [Alqur'aana] e yamiroore Amen. A anndaano ko woni Deftere, maa gom…óinal; si ko woni, Men wa…óunde ndaygu, ngu Men fewnirta on mo Men muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Amen …ìen. Pellet, ko a fewnoowo e laawol focciingol"
  42,53,"laawol Allah, On jey…óo ko woni kammuuli e ka leydi. Anndee, ko ka Allah, fiyakuuji …óin ruttotoo"
  43,1,"Haa, Miim"
  43,2,Mi woondirii Defere …ìanngunde nden
  43,3,"Men wa…óii nde janngeteende [e …óemngal] aarabu, belajo'o, on haqqilay"
  43,4,"Pellet, hinde woni ka Amen gaa, ka yumma Defte, toowunde, √±e√±aande"
  43,5,"E Men acciray jippinangol on jantoore nden, …óuurngal on, fii on wonii yim…ìe fantim…ìe"
  43,6,∆äuu…óii e Annabaa…ìe …ìe Men nuli e adinoo…ìe …ìen
  43,7,"Annabaajo araali e ma…ì…ìe, si wanaa …ìe jalkitay mo"
  43,8,Men halki ko …ìuri …ìe sa…ótude doole ! Toode mise adinoo…ìe …ìen yawtiino
  43,9,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike …ìe: \"Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin?\" ∆Åe wi'ay: \"Ko Foolu…óo, Anndu…óo On tagi …ói"
  43,10,"On wa…óiran…óo on leydi ndin weertaandi, O wa…óani on …óate e mayri, fii no …óoworon"
